Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑真的要走了么……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:11.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我吓到小白了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}因为看到小黑就觉得是小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}原来你可以变成人形啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}一直都没有想过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}还变的不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:25.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}小黑怎么会是白头发呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}啊 这个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:28.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}以前也是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}啊 小黑难道真的比爷爷还大？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不是不是 我也是十岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哈哈 那生日呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}定在十一月一号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}比我小耶 小黑是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:42.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}唔 定在？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:44.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯 我不知道自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:46.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}师父就给我选了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:49.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑是要回师父那了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不是我还有必须要完成的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那小黑还会回来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:56.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}当然 到时候也介绍师父给你认识
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}师父是这个世界上最好的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯！那要早点回来哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:02.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:16.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:18.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:21.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:26.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:29.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:32.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哥哥一直都知道小黑会走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是啊 他本来就是在这里养伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我有点想爸爸妈妈了……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈哈 他们一定会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:45.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小白啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:46.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你说什么！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我听不见！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}爷爷我去游泳啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:53.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:54.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}比丢~走！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:55.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}BIU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}要早点回来呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:01:59.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊 小黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:11.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我能借用一下会馆的传送系统吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}当然 您要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:13.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}龙游
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:14.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}您是准备去接下一项任务么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔 你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯 应该不用去龙游了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哟 小猫~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}别来无恙啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你怎么知道是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你没有见过我的人形吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我观察你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:38.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}还有那个小姑娘~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}别误会 别误会！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}她绝对不在我的狩猎许可范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:48.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我只是来借道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}馆长 那我自己上去喽~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:58.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}会馆允许狩猎人类么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:02.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他叫涅帕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是食人族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}食人族？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}对 所以我们会馆也没有立场阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}只能把狩猎范围规范在“恶人”的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}被狩猎的人必须带到这里经过我们的审核
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}难道他们不能吃其他的食物么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不行就像血族一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:23.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他们只能通过特定的食物来获取能量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们会尽量给他们提供死刑犯和罪大恶极的人的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:28.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}但相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果他们遭到人类的捕杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们也没有立场干预
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这样……可以么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:41.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}有什么办法呢？我们也不能剥夺他们的生存权力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:46.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}真要说的话 其实他们自己也是受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}人类就不用说了 很多妖精也不待见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}但是他们并没有选择权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那就这样让他自行去捕猎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:04:01.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不然呢？由我们准备还是像人类一样圈养食物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}前几天我在龙游碰到无限大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他在龙游吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不 他已经离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他让我见到您时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:17.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}把接下来的任务交给您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:24.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}帮我念念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}记得噢 明天早上十点开服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}一定不能迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}知道啦~你已经说很多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这可是游戏的革命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我保证你玩了以后就会疯狂的喜欢上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好啦好啦 我一定会准时联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你可千万记住啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}bye~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}拜拜~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:50.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}呼……一说起游戏就很啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:56.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我经常好几天没有见到山新 为什么不想她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}因为你知道去哪找她呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔……是噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哥哥 你说小黑什么时候会回来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他才走了一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}一天~说不定马上就回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}告别半天连一集都没撑到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哥哥你说话好像爷爷噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑你完成任务啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:19.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我是来做任务的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔？
